Ukraine’s Carbon-Dioxide Emissions Increased by 9.6% in First Quarter

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-05-30T11:52:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/ukraine-carbon-dioxide-emissions-rose-by-9-6-in-first-quarter.html
Ukraine’s emissions of carbon dioxide
increased by 9.6 percent in first three months of the year from
the year-earlier period to 53 million metric tons, the nation’s
statistics office said today.  Methane emissions in the January-March period rose 2.8
percent to 213,000 tons, the Kiev-based State Statistics
Committee said on its  website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
